						               													<description>Description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Scafford Gang is the most ruthless band of Mutant Outlaws in the Southwest! Their leader, Colonel Scafford, was a veteran of the Confederacy during the American Civil War, who turned to crime after the South fell. Fleeing West, he started a gang of ex-Confederates, thugs, and criminals, as well as his five sons. Making their hideouts up in the caves and mines around Brimstone, they have grown hideously mutated by the corrupting influence of the Dark Stone and the Void energies that pour out of every gateway opened to another world.&amp;#10;     &amp;#10;The Shadows of Brimstone: The Scafford Gang Deluxe Enemy Pack contains everything you need to add the nefarious Scafford Gang and their dastardly leader, Colonel Scafford, to your games of Shadows of Brimstone!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Included are 6 Scafford Gang models and 1 Colonel Scafford model to lead them into battle, the 2 large Enemy Record Sheets for them, a host of new cards themed around these ruthless Mutants &amp;mdash; including all of the Threat Cards needed to add them to your games, and 2 new Missions focusing on these deadly new Enemies!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;CONTENTS&amp;#10;1x rulebook with 2 new missions and painting guide&amp;#10;1x Colonel Scafford&amp;#10;6x Scafford Gang&amp;#10;2x large enemy record sheet&amp;#10;1x die-cut counter sheet&amp;#10;38x game cards: &amp;#10;&amp;#10;    13x threat cards&amp;#10;    5x scafford lieutenant cards&amp;#10;    5x mine encounter cards&amp;#10;    6x gear cards&amp;#10;    8x hideous mutation cards&amp;#10;    1x shootout card&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
